XXXVII\. PHŒNIX, a great marquis, appears like the bird of that name,
singing dulcet notes in a child's voice. <span
id="fr_220"></span>[2](#fn_219.md) When he assumes human shape at the will
of the Magician, he speaks marvellously of all sciences, proves an
excellent poet and fulfils orders admirably. He hopes to return to the
Seventh Thrones in 1200 years.

<span id="img_20702"></span> [![](tn/generic.jpg)  
Click to view](img/20702.jpg.md)  
THE SEAL OF HALPAS

XXXVIII\. HALPAS, a great earl, appears in the form of a stockdove,
speaking with a hoarse voice. He burns towns, <span
id="fr_221"></span>[3](#fn_220.md)

<span id="page_208">p. 208</span>

visits the wicked with the sword and can send men to fields of war or to
other places.

